{"ts":"2026-06-29T10:10:55.262Z","tool":"execute_code","type":"tool","status":"ERROR","ms":926,"action":"execute","params":{"action":"execute","code":"var runtime = UnityEngine.GameObject.Find(\"CatLifeRuntime\");\nif (runtime == null)\n{\n    runtime = new UnityEngine.GameObject(\"CatLifeRuntime\");\n}\n\nvar stateMachine = runtime.GetComponent<CatLife.Core.StateMachine>();\nif (stateMachine == null)\n{\n    stateMachine = runtime.AddComponent<CatLife.Core.StateMachine>();\n}\n\nvar demo = runtime.GetComponent<CatLife.Cat.CatAnimationMvpDemo>();\nif (demo == null)\n{\n    demo = runtime.AddComponent<CatLife.Cat.CatAnimationMvpDemo>();\n}\n\nvar so = new UnityEditor.SerializedObject(demo);\nvar stateMachineProp = so.FindProperty(\"stateMachine\");\nif (stateMachineProp != null) stateMachineProp.objectReferenceValue = stateMachine;\nvar playOnStart = so.FindProperty(\"playOnStart\");\nif (playOnStart != null) playOnStart.boolValue = true;\nvar loop = so.FindProperty(\"loop\");\nif (loop != null) loop.boolValue = true;\nvar stateDuration = so.FindProperty(\"stateDuration\");\nif (stateDuration != null) stateDuration.floatValue = 3f;\nso.ApplyModifiedProperties();\n\nUnityEditor.EditorUtility.SetDirty(runtime);\nUnityEditor.SceneManagement.EditorSceneManager.MarkSceneDirty(runtime.scene);\nreturn \"Configured CatLifeRuntime with StateMachine and CatAnimationMvpDemo\";","safety_checks":true},"error":"Compilation failed"}
